cli_content:
interface: Ethernet0/0
    Crypto map tag: VPN1, local addr 192.168.1.1
     protected vrf: (none)
     local  ident (addr/mask/prot/port): (10.0.0.1/255.255.255.0/47/0)
     remote ident (addr/mask/prot/port): (10.0.1.1/255.255.255.0/47/0)
     current_peer 192.168.2.1 port 500
       PERMIT, flags={origin_is_acl,}
    #pkts encaps: 100, #pkts encrypt: 100, #pkts digest: 100
    #pkts decaps: 100, #pkts decrypt: 100, #pkts verify: 100
    #pkts compressed: 0, #pkts decompressed: 0
    #pkts not compressed: 0, #pkts not decompressed: 0
    #pkts internal err: 0, #pkts replay error: 0
textfsm_template:
Value INTERFACE (\S+)
Value CRYPTO_MAP_TAG (\S+)
Value LOCAL_ADDR (\d{1,3}(?:\.\d{1,3}){3})
Value VRF (\w+)
Value LOCAL_IDENT (\(\S+\))
Value REMOTE_IDENT (\(\S+\))
Value CURRENT_PEER (\d{1,3}(?:\.\d{1,3}){3})
Value PERMIT (\w+)
Value ENCAPS (\d+)
Value ENCRYPT (\d+)
Value DIGEST (\d+)
Value DECAPS (\d+)
Value DECRYPT (\d+)
Value VERIFY (\d+)
Value COMPRESSED (\d+)
Value DECOMPRESSED (\d+)
Value NOT_COMPRESSED (\d+)
Value NOT_DECOMPRESSED (\d+)
Value INTERNAL_ERR (\d+)
Value REPLAY_ERROR (\d+)

Start
  ^interface: ${INTERFACE}$$
  ^\s*Crypto map tag: ${CRYPTO_MAP_TAG}, local addr ${LOCAL_ADDR}$$
  ^\s*protected vrf: ${VRF}$$
  ^\s*local  ident \(addr/mask/prot/port\): ${LOCAL_IDENT}$$
  ^\s*remote ident \(addr/mask/prot/port\): ${REMOTE_IDENT}$$
  ^\s*current_peer ${CURRENT_PEER} port \d+$$
  ^\s*${PERMIT}, flags=\{\w+,\}$$
  ^\s*#pkts encaps: ${ENCAPS}, #pkts encrypt: ${ENCRYPT}, #pkts digest: ${DIGEST}$$
  ^\s*#pkts decaps: ${DECAPS}, #pkts decrypt: ${DECRYPT}, #pkts verify: ${VERIFY}$$
  ^\s*#pkts compressed: ${COMPRESSED}, #pkts decompressed: ${DECOMPRESSED}$$
  ^\s*#pkts not compressed: ${NOT_COMPRESSED}, #pkts not decompressed: ${NOT_DECOMPRESSED}$$
  ^\s*#pkts internal err: ${INTERNAL_ERR}, #pkts replay error: ${REPLAY_ERROR}$$ -> Record
